            "failure_message": "Requires a noticeable rise into contentment plus a competence signature (agency_control and mild pride/confidence) while threat stays low. Triggers only when arousal or engagement drops sharply (the ‘task finished’ downshift). Blocks big-win states (triumph/euphoria) and keeps relief/stress from dominating so it reads like earned closure, not danger passing or white-knuckle effort."
